{"tid":1979023,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同屋企人溝通唔到，可以點","createTime":"2020-04-19T06:37:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T08:10:43.000Z","uid":344619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"67d933b361dac6b81f59a1e5f1d9920684438f7d","tid":1979023,"uid":344619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:37:28.000Z","msg":"每次都唔聽人解釋<br />\n次次都覺得係我問題<br />\n永遠都係佢地啱唒<br />\n明明我有做嘅事，又屈我話我冇做<br />\n又話我成日唔出聲 唔同佢哋溝通<br />\n但唔係個個都咁talkative㗎喎<br />\n我比較中意做聆聽者啫。<br />\n況且 我中意傾/玩嘅嘢佢哋又唔識<br />\n我已經次次同佢地一齊去親戚屋企<br />\n我自問已經好有禮貌 做得好好<br />\n但我本身比較內斂 對住唔熟嘅人少啲講嘢<br />\n我已經盡量搭嘴，但咁大代溝我唔知可以主動講啲咩<br />\n但佢哋都唔明<br />\n成日鬧我，我解釋佢又唔聽，<br />\n究竟我可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d05d7916162ff93af47a3ea4cd70c6f285f83ab","tid":1979023,"uid":345989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:38:27.000Z","msg":"Same as I"},{"pid":"1af54b68ab1c4f0ac290b0198ae8e5667f765047","tid":1979023,"uid":38440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:40:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"995aa0c569e492288641130ca923d1afc7faf9d3","tid":1979023,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1af54b68ab1c4f0ac290b0198ae8e5667f765047","tid":1979023,"uid":38440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:40:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:43:44.000Z","msg":"了解到就唔叫溝通唔到啦"},{"pid":"499dcb12fcfbff83c7cad2832e0cd743b08f420f","tid":1979023,"uid":344619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1af54b68ab1c4f0ac290b0198ae8e5667f765047","tid":1979023,"uid":38440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:40:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:46:18.000Z","msg":"有，因為每次佢哋鬧我 都會講點解咁諗我<br />\n所以我每次解釋返，我並唔係咁諗<br />\n但佢哋都係唔肯接受我嘅解釋，唔肯聽"},{"pid":"e65c99b24abda883f01a0983cb10482cb4474683","tid":1979023,"uid":344619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d05d7916162ff93af47a3ea4cd70c6f285f83ab","tid":1979023,"uid":345989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:38:27.000Z","msg":"Same as I"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:46:48.000Z","msg":"What can I do <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70cfee68f016fcd87be8b56bf10850a3dbb25efe","tid":1979023,"uid":344619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"995aa0c569e492288641130ca923d1afc7faf9d3","tid":1979023,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1af54b68ab1c4f0ac290b0198ae8e5667f765047","tid":1979023,"uid":38440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:40:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:43:44.000Z","msg":"了解到就唔叫溝通唔到啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:48:26.000Z","msg":"有了解，之後我解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但佢哋都唔聽，覺得係歪理。我真係冇嘢好講"},{"pid":"5ab485df2303cfe025023bb73ff48eec46e1d037","tid":1979023,"uid":152387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T08:10:43.000Z","msg":"通常唔想/唔識同人溝通<br />\n我都會用微笑代替"}]}